<h2 id="分支说明">分支说明</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>分支</th>
          <th>用途</th>
          <th>操作对象</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td><strong>master</strong></td>
          <td>存储博客源码</td>
          <td>你写文章、提交代码的地方</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td><strong>gh-pages</strong></td>
          <td>存储构建产物</td>
          <td>GitHub Actions 自动部署，<strong>不要手动操作</strong></td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>重要：永远只操作 master 分支，不要手动提交到 gh-pages 分支！</strong></p>
<hr>
<h2 id="快速上手">快速上手</h2>
<h3 id="第一步写文章">第一步：写文章</h3>
<ol>
<li>进入文章目录：<code>D:\blog\andrea\content\posts</code></li>
<li>新建 <code>.md</code> 文件（或用命令创建：<code>hugo new posts/文章名.md</code>）</li>
<li>文件开头添加 Front Matter：</li>
</ol>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-toml">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-toml" data-lang="toml"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="err">+++</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nx">date</span> <span class="p">=</span> <span class="s1">&#39;2026-03-20T10:00:00+08:00&#39;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nx">draft</span> <span class="p">=</span> <span class="kc">false</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nx">title</span> <span class="p">=</span> <span class="s1">&#39;文章标题&#39;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="err">+++</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<ol start="4">
<li>在 <code>+++</code> 下方用 Markdown 写正文</li>
<li>图片放在文章同级目录，引用方式：<code>![描述](图片名.jpg)</code></li>
</ol>
<h3 id="第二步本地预览可选">第二步：本地预览（可选）</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-bash">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nb">cd</span> D:<span class="se">\b</span>log<span class="se">\a</span>ndrea
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">hugo server -D
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 浏览器访问 http://localhost:1313</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># Ctrl+C 停止服务</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="第三步发布到网站">第三步：发布到网站</h3>
